						               													<description>Drug Attack&amp;#10;Springboard to Family Communications&amp;#10;An informative game on drug abuse&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Something unseen is happening in your community now! Are you aware of the drug culture? How does drug abuse affect your community, your family? What can be done about the problem? Solutions are necessary here and now!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The answer to these problems await you when you play Drug Attack. Learn how to identify and help drug abusers. Learn how to cope with criminal drug pushers.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Drug Attack involves you as a Mayor, Health Officer, or Agent striving to save their community from a drug disaster. Together, they must detect the attack, meet it, and treat its victims.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Drug Attack is being played in schools throughout the United States. It is an ideal game for establishing family communication on the subject of drugs. It is a game of urgency -- a game of today!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
